==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncomeatable
<hw>Un`come*at"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not to be
come at, or reached; inaccessible.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>
<rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My honor is infallible and <qex>uncomeatable</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Congreve.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncomely</ent>⟦br⟧
